# game/remy1.rpy:1631
translate Korean remyoffmenu_a9e06be0:

    # c "Back home, we used to have computers everywhere. Most of us even carried one on our wrist wherever we went."
    c "우리 세계에선 컴퓨터가 어디에나 있어요. 심지어 대부분은 가는 곳 마다 하나씩 들고다니죠."

# game/remy1.rpy:1632
translate Korean remyoffmenu_5cdba81c:

    # Ry "Is that so?"
    Ry "정말요?"

# game/remy1.rpy:1638
translate Korean remyoffmenu_9cfe5f5f:

    # Ry "Oh, that means the library will be closing pretty soon. If you want to do or ask anything in particular, now is the time."
    Ry "아, 곧 도서관이 문을 닫을 시간이네요. 따로 물어보고 싶으신 게 있으면, 지금 물어보셔야할 것 같아요."

# game/remy1.rpy:1643
translate Korean remyoffmenu_41a3bce8:

    # Ry "There's a lot we could get into, but I'm afraid we won't have enough time now. Maybe another day."
    Ry "말씀드릴 수 있는 건 많은데, 지금은 별로 시간이 많은 것 같지 않네요. 나중에 말씀드릴게요."

# game/remy1.rpy:1647
translate Korean remyoffmenu_fdd8b5c2:

    # Ry "What do you mean by that?"
    Ry "그게 무슨 말씀이세요?"

# game/remy1.rpy:1648
translate Korean remyoffmenu_fd77ed04:

    # c "You know, for a relationship."
