# game/remy1.rpy:1650
translate Korean remyoffmenu_d916458e:

    # Ry "That is... If you are going to ask me like that, my answer is going to be no."
    Ry "그게... 그렇게 물어보시면, 제 답은 아니오에요."

# game/remy1.rpy:1653
translate Korean remyoffmenu_bc0348b2:

    # Ry "I guess it's time to go, then. I'd rather not annoy the other employees by staying longer than we should."
    Ry "그럼 이제 가봐야 할 것 같네요. 우리가 여깄다간 다른 직원들이 짜증나할테니까요."

# game/remy1.rpy:1657
translate Korean remyoffmenu_d1c0ea4d:

    # Ry "Anyways, thank you for your help. This certainly was an... informative... meeting."
    Ry "아무튼, 도와주셔서 고마워요. 이건 확실히... 유익한... 만남이었네요."

# game/remy1.rpy:1663
